//Write a program to find reverse of a number using function with argumentsâ€¦

int main()
{
    int n;
    printf("\n enter N:");
    scanf("%d",&n);
    void reverse(int n);
    reverse(n);
}
void reverse(n)
{
    int r,rev=0;
    while(n!=0)
    {
        r=n%10;
        rev=rev*10+r;
        n=n/10;
    }
    printf("\n reverse of the number=%d",rev);
}


Output:
enter N:456

 reverse of the number=654

Reference:https://funcodepro.blogspot.com/2018/12/how-to-reverse-any-number-using.html
